  <li id="comment-24101" class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/14595773202850589330" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">riorita</a></cite></div>
