    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>To make this salad authentically Russian (I am a Russian and only recently moved to the US), go with the sunflower oil and Russian mustard, which is so-ooo different from Dijon mustard. If you buy both in a Russian market (I am not working for any), you&#39;ll see the difference and you&#39;ll love them. And, btw, the sunflower oil is full of vitamin E!</p>
