      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/05/pile-it-on/#comment-24148"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-06-21T21:35:01-04:00">Tuesday, June 21, 2011 at 9:35 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I am a HUGE egg lover and my husband is crazy for mushrooms so I thought this would be a perfect fit for us!  I made homemade buns and it looked heavenly, but to both of us it just tasted like&#8230; potato salad made with mushrooms instead of potato.  In fact several times I caught myself thinking &#8220;I should add some potato.&#8221;  Not that that made it unpleasant in any way, I just think I prefer my egg salad significantly more eggy, and my potato salad more potato-y.</p>
    </div>

